text:
Hehe... I ordered the morning set.
It feels like a dream morning activity, doesn't it...?

Hey...
I wish it would come soon...

It's still early...
Usually, I'd still be at home by now...

Today, we have a lot of time
even after this, right...?

Yeah, after we finish eating,
let's head to the practice studio for self-training──!
It was really delicious, wasn't it...?

Ahaha, after eating so much,
I'm starting to feel sleepy.

Are you feeling sleepy too, Hana-chan...? Maybe
it's because of the effort we put into waking up early...

I might order
an additional wake-up coffee...!
